Package: ondisc
Title: Algorithms for large, sparse, single-cell expression matrices
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Timothy", "Barry", , "tbarry2@andrew.cmu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: `ondisc` implements space- and time-optimal algorithms for manipulating and querying large, sparse, single-cell expression matrices. `ondisc` facilitates out-of-core and distributed analysis of single-cell data, with a special focus on single-cell CRISPR screens.
